---
title: Honey-Garlic Chicken and Veggie Noodles with Broccoli  and Cashews
description: These noodles will make you think twice about ordering takeout! Slightly sweet and definitely savoury, with a touch of unctuousness from plant-based mayo and loads of veggies, this noodle dish can satisfy even the hungriest of appetites!
